punniya boomi is a 1978 indian tamil film , directed by k. vijayan and produced by n. v. ramasamy . the film stars sivaji ganesan , vanisri , sangeeta , m. n. nambiar and v. k. ramasamy in lead roles . the film had musical score by m. s. viswanathan . the film was a remake of mother india . the film was also remade in telugu as bangaru thalli .